{"tid":336950,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"入泥屌醒我唔該","createTime":"2017-07-27T00:54:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-28T16:46:37.000Z","uid":131249,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7b8db01c659e43e215416f6483ec72c91adfabe1","tid":336950,"uid":131249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T00:54:04.000Z","msg":"借朋友a/c一用發洩下 因為自己fb用唔到<br />\n<br />\n好多野內心明明有答案但係好唔想接受 講就容易做就好難 就好似你明知對方呃你 但係你都心甘情願好想佢繼續呃你咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n明明做錯既係佢 但係點解到最後講分手既係佢 好後悔自己拆穿左佢既真面目 不斷喺度諗 如果當時無拆穿佢 而家我地會唔會仲可以好似以前咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仍然難禁 看著你這個壞人 有甚麼的吸引 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"555b31ee27cbebb099efea0ae26f382588839306","tid":336950,"uid":30377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T00:54:58.000Z","msg":"呢D野冇得屌醒 要靠自己柒到一個地步就會醒"},{"pid":"7fe9a1b6f7ada7e0e84396aebcdbc411672e20ff","tid":336950,"uid":131249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T00:56:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢D野冇得屌醒 要靠自己柒到一個地步就會醒</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n已經柒緊 有搵番佢 點先可以阻止自己唔好再係咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ece1984fb863c02f0089e5021c2e34cc2d059d93","tid":336950,"uid":130575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T00:56:43.000Z","msg":"自己都唔想醒，人地又點會叫得醒"},{"pid":"fd37b7214e3c74a3dfc5948aec5e350afbe5d22e","tid":336950,"uid":50483,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T00:58:24.000Z","msg":"泥你老母個臭閪咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdf66cf201455933084e81b07458ccbcdb7df711","tid":336950,"uid":30377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T00:58:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>呢D野冇得屌醒 要靠自己<span style=\"color: red;\">柒到一個地步</span>就會醒</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n已經柒緊 有搵番佢 點先可以阻止自己唔好再係咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌咁係咪叫你唔好搵你就唔搵先?講幾多野都冇用<br />\n如果勸真係有用 呢個世界死少好多人<br />\n呢啲事要靠自己諗通 如果唔係講到渴撚死你都未明"},{"pid":"562087f255e5028d006addec79e2512cb495b086","tid":336950,"uid":131249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T00:59:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>自己都唔想醒，人地又點會叫得醒</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點解你要令我由唔信人變返信人 到最後又要比我發現原來一直都係呃緊我 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa22585440c1bc9281e28ac50f521baaa8917e8a","tid":336950,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T01:00:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"eabad0b41132112d3ead7ef61a8f0548452e6df7","tid":336950,"uid":131249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T01:02:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">泥<span style=\"color: red;\">✗ <strong>嚟</strong></span><br />\n野<span style=\"color: red;\">✗ <strong>嘢</strong></span><br />\n既<span style=\"color: red;\">✗ <strong>嘅</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>宜使用標點符號。</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/XpQR3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FXpQR3.png&h=0ced7f69&s={SIZE}\" /></span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n對唔住 我會改 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e45fc8f4867a58551808e057c0dbb0d7b61fab8b","tid":336950,"uid":61896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T01:33:12.000Z","msg":"泥你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50d8205996fd3d59bbf5c2f94807cfad15e38339","tid":336950,"uid":131249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T16:46:37.000Z","msg":"而家我冇搵佢，係佢搵我，好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}